  "body": "### Overview\r\nI wanted to add more ETH to the test accounts, and needed to set the -e flag in ganache\r\nI noticed it was cutting out the extra commands, but could be added\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\n\r\nbrownie-config.yaml\r\n\r\n```\r\nnetwork:\r\n   networks:\r\n       development:\r\n            test_rpc:\r\n                cmd: ganache-cli\r\n                extra_param: \"-e  10000\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nor \r\n\r\n```\r\nnetwork:\r\n   networks:\r\n       development:\r\n            test_rpc:\r\n                cmd: \"ganache-cli -e 10000\"\r\n                \r\n```\r\n\r\notherwise less generally\r\n \r\n```\r\nnetwork:\r\n   networks:\r\n       development:\r\n            test_rpc:\r\n                cmd: ganache-cli\r\n                default_eth: 10000\r\n```\r\n",
